@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gthkiw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((wp.sin(v2 + 0.35) - (v2 + 0.54 * v1 + 0.98)) * wp.exp(0.35))
    v1 = (0.88 - wp.abs((tmp + 0.55 * tmp + 0.78)))
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.abs(wp.abs(v1 + 0.71)))
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.sin((tmp + 0.49 - v1 + 0.18)))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.exp((tmp + 0.81 + v2 + 0.40)))
    tmp = (wp.abs(v1) - wp.abs((v0 + 0.13 + v0 + 0.75)))
    data[tid] = v0
